dBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:58:59.000Z","msg":"推到8.5<br />\n唔好會借口自己"},{"pid":"721144e9274069c361d2a881e81932b39013217a","tid":1385183,"uid":253573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:24:40.000Z","msg":"8.5見"},{"pid":"e811c2b5932a0abf4f3f24ee8abac120df502b68","tid":1385183,"uid":187757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:52:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde20f364b1459ff3f2ff13fe401390288f53636","tid":1385183,"uid":187757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:52:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b76b56c230b6f20d71329fa0b03159df618f3c","tid":1385183,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:52:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5b73f082fa1fa67c3d938fe4fff623f97da90719","tid":1385183,"uid":187757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f808d1dd2a516658ac07fa7e979761889fa2a549","tid":1385183,"uid":191656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38efda87dd714a53613ab999e7d7c81e62ea3f57","tid":1385183,"uid":187757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:24:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲唔出黎等幾時</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你話你怕死怕乜怕物唔想出黎，咁罷工拎日假 做到啦掛？而家病都唔比咩？又唔洗你露面，又可以叫做略盡小小棉力。<br />\n<br />\n眼見公司朋友同事有好多都會屌個政府無能，話200萬大遊行政府都唔撚回應，睇到近日新聞又話黑警可恥。<br />\n但，屌！尋日出消息話今日車長罷工 個撚個驚到乜咁，又話死啦點番工啊，佢地真心係驚。屌，有冇咁撚大責任，有冇咁撚奴性鍾意番工？你話做醫生就話 冇左你真係可能救唔到人姐，平凡打工仔一個 真係驚閪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大佬你有一日半日係條街200萬人和平行街，有咩好怕，一於當你透明。<br />\n但如果，<br />\n起碼嗰200萬人都肯8.5一齊罷工，我相信真係可以開始令政府覺得事態嚴重。先唔好話你份工你公司影唔影響到政府運作，做咗先。十間公司影響唔到，一百間一千間一定影響到。<br />\n一句講晒，前線用條命為你地出黎同政府抗爭，你輕輕為佢地付出一日假期even一日人工，得唔得？如果你呢樣咁小事都做唔到，將來萬一真係抗爭唔成功，你無資格出聲。<br />\n<br />\n醒覺未？<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">FREEDOM IS NOT FREE</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:53:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ed4c203aac88fa541ec14a47e915ec182275fc","tid":1385183,"uid":228656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:53:25.000Z","msg":"[突發]香港新challenge<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1386405\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1386405</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8f34d610eb46ad52392c4c3256266292f08e0ef0","tid":1385183,"uid":187757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:54:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/me66zNX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fme66zNX.png&h=4aeb1df5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc776d4fd72962d741d3327ac02626684fd41b68","tid":1385183,"uid":187757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d15fe73008414a51808fe2ef5064e055c8ca674f","tid":1385183,"uid":187757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"