r />\n<br />\n因此，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"225f9747301f5bf2b0f948073509a6a425e75991","tid":1385183,"uid":243896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:15:06.000Z","msg":"85 罷工"},{"pid":"d3700c973fa2aa719d905cc61715922a6d502112","tid":1385183,"uid":187757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:50:06.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"e950218050b896228e5d479c86b37bdb46ac7644","tid":1385183,"uid":187757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51cdaaa44a2de083de4f7b6fc32420bf24bcba1b","tid":1385183,"uid":187757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:52:12.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"8faa1b4876be252454fe14b2be607f0cdb517de8","tid":1385183,"uid":187757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:52:22.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"3c4b21e6ab9bfdd4fe3889d3eb5a840c72825b33","tid":1385183,"uid":252973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:52:46.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人<br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷<br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"ec2bb12d71b8419b9eb13b8239fe61a1d10befcc","tid":1385183,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:53:00.000Z","msg":"我覺得派傳單威力最大<br />\n612 都係派傳單做到出黎"},{"pid":"675d0b18ba17165b54caee1fa8c7f1e4abd0d565","tid":1385183,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ffe5bac2d23c4b3be70f615a8ab16b7b304a058","tid":1385183,"uid":231594,"like":0,"d